&lt;li>在文件管理器中打开刚才解压的文件，并在地址栏输入 cmd 回车进入Windows命令窗口；&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>&lt;figure>&lt;a class="lightgallery" href="http://blog.hifo.fun/posts/c5ef51d/pics/cmd.webp?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/c5ef51d/pics/cmd.webp?size=small" data-sub-html="&lt;h2>cmd&lt;/h2>&lt;p>cmd&lt;/p>">&lt;img loading="lazy" src="http://blog.hifo.fun/posts/c5ef51d/pics/cmd.webp" alt="cmd" srcset="http://blog.hifo.fun/posts/c5ef51d/pics/cmd.webp?size=small, http://blog.hifo.fun/posts/c5ef51d/pics/cmd.webp?size=medium 1.5x, http://blog.hifo.fun/posts/c5ef51d/pics/cmd.webp?size=large 2x" data-title="cmd" style="--width: 968px;--aspect-ratio: 968 / 742;background: url(/images/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/>&lt;/a>&lt;figcaption class="image-caption">cmd&lt;/figcaption>
 &lt;/figure>&lt;/p>
